FBIS4-56502 "drlat087_c_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-087 Daily Report 3 May 1994 MEXICO New Public Security Director Takes Office New Public Security Director Takes Office PA0505000394 Mexico City XEW Television Network in Spanish 0430 GMT 3 May 94 PA0505000394 Mexico City XEW Television Network Spanish BFN [From the "24 Hours" newscast] [Text] Victor Manuel Vasquez Fernandez took over today as new director of public security of Tijuana, replacing Federico Benitez, who was murdered last Thursday.
